name: Moo Moo Yahoo!
description:
Aliens have come to kidnap you!! Use your utters as... weapons?  Based on the common trope of aliens kidnapping cows, Moo Moo Wahoo! is an endless arcade shoot em' up based on old arcade titles, have fun and aim for the high score! https://liluo.io/leokidd/moo-moo-wahoo- (liluo link)

Sound, Programming, and graphics all done by me!

Voice Lines done by ChiliCheeseCake
